{"id":509837,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":4,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"纪念“五一”国际劳动节","genre":"","count":"208","ytitle":"","mtitle":"船台春歌","ftitle":"","authors":["钱国梁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红造船厂　钱国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞飞，红日照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声响彻浦江潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万个浪头呼声急:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江欢腾迎春到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵东风扑面来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台处处春喧闹:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤响雷声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电焊金雨浇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耸天高吊舒钢腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风展红旗呼啦啦飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船工，绣春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千江万岭朝这儿瞧:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍拍铁肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起钢山站云霄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥挥擎天手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推着巨轮下水了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花飞溅拍云天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩旗狂舞染江涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台春色分外娇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛高亢唱不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情澎湃歌如潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯歌声声飞北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席点头向咱笑!"}]}